                                "description": "\n\n\n\u003cp\u003enote: hotel was previously named Grand Cakra Hotel\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eLocation\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nGrand Cakra Hotel Malang is located in area / city Blimbing.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eAbout Grand Cakra Hotel Malang\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\nFrom business event to corporate gathering, Grand Cakra Hotel Malang provides complete services and facilities that you and your colleagues need.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nWhether you are planning an event or other special occasions, Grand Cakra Hotel Malang is a great choice for you with a large and well-equipped function room to suit your requirements.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nHave fun with various entertaining facilities for you and the whole family at Grand Cakra Hotel Malang, a wonderful accommodation for your family holiday.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nThis hotel is an ideal choice for you, novice to professional golfers.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nThis hotel is the perfect choice for couples seeking a romantic getaway or a honeymoon retreat. Enjoy the most memorable nights with your loved one by staying at Grand Cakra Hotel Malang.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nIf you plan to have a long-term stay, staying at Grand Cakra Hotel Malang is the right choice for you. Providing wide range of facilities and great service quality, this accommodation certainly makes you feel at home.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nAre you a shopaholic? Staying at Grand Cakra Hotel Malang will surely spoil you for numerous shopping centers nearby.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nWhile traveling with friends can be a lot of fun, traveling solo has its own perks. As for the accommodation, Grand Cakra Hotel Malang is suitable for you who value privacy during your stay.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nSpa treatment is one of the main features of the hotel. Pamper yourself with the relaxing treatment that rejuvenates you.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\nBe ready to get the unforgettable stay experience by its exclusive service, completed by a full range of facilities to cater all your needs.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe hotel’s fitness center is a must-try during your stay here.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHave an enjoyable and relaxing day at the pool, whether you’re traveling solo or with your loved ones.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGet the best deal for finest quality of spa treatment to unwind and rejuvenate yourself.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e24-hours front desk is available to serve you, from check-in to check-out, or any assistance you need. Should you desire more, do not hesitate to ask the front desk, we are always ready to accommodate you.\u003c/p\u003e\n \n\u003cp\u003eSavor your favorite dishes with special cuisines from Grand Cakra Hotel Malang exclusively for you.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWiFi is available within public areas of the property to help you to stay connected with family and friends.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGrand Cakra Hotel Malang is a hotel with great comfort and excellent service according to most hotel's guests.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n  Enjoy luxurious treats and incomparable experience by staying at Grand Cakra Hotel Malang.\n\u003c/p\u003e",
                                "overview": "\n\n\n\u003cp\u003enote: hotel was previously named Grand Cakra Hotel\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\nGrand Cakra Hotel Malang is located in area / city Blimbing.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e24-hours front desk is available to serve you, from check-in to check-out, or any assistance you need. Should you desire more, do not hesitate to ask the front desk, we are always ready to accommodate you.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWiFi is available within public areas of the property to help you to stay connected with family and friends.\u003c/p\u003e\n",
                                "propertyInformation": null,
                                "areaInformation": null,
                                "hotelPolicy": "\n\n\n\n            \u003cp\u003e  \n        Accommodation charges IDR 110,000/guest for extra breakfast.\n        \u003c/p\u003e\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n            \u003cp\u003e  \n                    Breakfast at the accommodation will be provided from 06:00 - 10:00.\n                \u003c/p\u003e\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n    \tSmoking is allowed only in the designated smoking area.\n\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \u003cp\u003e \n            Pets are not allowed in the accommodation.      \n        \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\tAirport transfer is available for IDR 70,000/person.\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t    \n\n\n",
